<p>Important Note: In the code below you only have to write the match construct. Assume that _a is the first number, _operator is the operator and _b is the second number.</p>

<p>For any invalid operator passed as input the program should print invalid</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>fn test(a: i32, operator: char, b: i32) {
   // Write code here
}

</code></pre></div></div>
